This folder contains the flux observation files to be used for the full "multi-site" calibrations in Phase 1b. 

THe files include NEE, Qle and Qh variables and their uncertainties.

Please see the protocol and/or site information pdf in this folder for information on PFT type and percent cover, soil layer depths and soil texture (percent sand, silt and clay) for each layer (where available).

Full information on the sources of PFT and soil information will be documented in the CalLMIP Phase 1 protocol paper.
